  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1654_dai_lns235ms_c_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <persName ref="#dianatKhan">دیانت خان</persName>
               مرید حضرت
               <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جھان</persName>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#dianatKhan">Dianat Khan</persName>, disciple of Lord <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName></mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>چودھری پرگنہ  
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دھار</placeName>
               از صوبہ
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوہ</placeName>
               را اعلام آنکہ چون حقیقت دولت خواھی و نیک سلوکی
               <lb/>او سیادت و نقابت پناہ  وزارت و متعالی و نگاہ محبت و مودب اطوار 
               <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">میر ابراھیم</persName>
               بسیار
               <lb/>باینجانب نوشتہ بودند کہ در تردد زراعت  فصل ربیع وغیرہ نھایت سعی دارد 
               <lb/>بنا بران نوشتہ می شود کہ ھمبرین نمط در تردد زراعت و وصول مال واجبی 
               <lb/>ساعی بودہ آنچنان احتیاط بکار برد کہ مال سرکار بوقت عاید شود 
               <lb/>و زراعت و آبادانی روزبروز افزون گردد و خاطر خواہ شود 
               <lb/>کہ موافق خدمات حسنہ بہ نتایج نیک سرافرازی خواھد یافت و دزدان را کہ 
               <lb/>آوردہ  بسیادت و نقابت پناہ  
               <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">میر</persName> 
               مشار الیہ رجوع نمودہ مجری او بسیار شد
               <lb/>خاطر خود جمع  داشتہ درین باب خود را معاف  بدارد
               بتاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus">
               <num>۲۷</num>
               شھر محرم 
               سنه
               <num>٢٨</num>
               </date>
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>It is indicated to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName> that since the facts about his loyalty and good behaviour<lb/> 
               have been written by that Refuge of Lordliness and Excellence and Ministry and Exaltation and Care of Love and Friendship <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">Mir Ibrahim</persName><lb/>   
               to me, that in the improvement of agriculture for the spring harvest etc., he [you] made a great deal of effort.<lb/>
               On this basis, let it be written that [by] continuing to make such efforts in the organizing of agriculture and the collection of the taxes due,<lb/>
               [you] pay such attention to work that the taxes of the government are collected on time<lb/>
               and the agriculture and habitation increases day by day, and it shall be desired<lb/>
               that according to good service, he [you] be glorified by good results. And the thieves that<lb/>
               [you] had brought and lodged with the said <persName ref="#mirIbrahim">Mir [Ibrahim]</persName>, your work was well executed.<lb/>
               Being settled in mind, [you] should consider himself excused in this matter. 27 Muharram of the year <date calendar="#julus">28</date>. <g ref="#baiz">Ended</g>.
            </p>   
         </div> 
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1654_dai_lns235ms_c_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p><unclear>پروانه</unclear> <gap></gap></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p><unclear><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref></unclear> <gap></gap> </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               نقل گرفتہ شد
               <lb rend="empty"/>
            <app><rdg cert="low">ف</rdg> <rdg cert="medium">د</rdg></app>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6">
            <p>Copy taken.<note>The precise meaning of the single letter under this note is unclear.</note></p>
         </div>
